title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Gear Talk - METZ
description:
In this first episode of "Gear Talk" presented by Guitar Center, Toronto-based band METZ talk to fans about their gear, answering the episodes standard five questions, and sharing the detailed gear-focus of the three band-members.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
